metadata.description: The very first Music NFT launchpad and metaverse for Rock and Metal Music Bands! Rock'n'Verse will be the meeting point of rock and metal music bands, solo artists, music lovers and fan groups from all over the world. The first project of Rock'n'Verse is coming with an exclusive NFT serie on rock concept as 3333 pieces: SkinRunners! We are gonna ROCK it!
